# Welcome To Notebook

_Your Personal Smart Notebook System_

Notebook offers an HTML render system for note taking and report writing. It includes integrated LaText and standard HTML5 functionality.

## LaText

To integrate LaText into your Notebook, double dollar signs ($$) must wrapped around the equation. For example:

`
$$1+1=2 $$
`

__Output:__

$$
1+1=2
$$
